in the arena.)

36
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:10,640
(This Haotian Sect disciple)

37
00:02:10,760 --> 00:02:12,550
(is quite the extraordinaire.)

38
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:14,990
My great king.

39
