- Good!
- That's right!

48
00:03:46,830 --> 00:03:47,830
There's one more alive.

49
00:03:48,710 --> 00:03:54,550
- Kill him!
- Kill him!

50
00:03:54,790 --> 00:03:56,950
Please, don't kill me.

51
00:03:57,550 --> 00:03:59,920
I'm begging you, don't kill me.

52
