54
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:05,920
The state he is in now

55
00:04:07,710 --> 00:04:09,200
is no different from a dead man.

56
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:10,600
According to the rules,

57
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,760
they must be truly dead.

58
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:14,270
If he doesn't die

59
00:04:14,510 --> 00:04:15,550
and leaves that door,

60
00:04:15,710 --> 00:04:17,640
The Netherworld King
will sentence you to death.

61
00:04:17,710 --> 00:04:18,440
Please...

62
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:27,910
That should've been the way.

63
00:04:27,910 --> 00:04:28,390
Yeah.

64
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:31,120
Congratulations to No. 9528 for winning.

65
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:35,640
- Nice!
- Good!

66
00:04:37,250 --> 00:04:38,460
You should've just killed him.

67
00:04:38,470 --> 00:04:39,080
Good work.

68
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:39,800
Good!

69
00:04:39,950 --> 00:04:41,030
He is really skilled.

70
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:33,800
- Kill him!
- Kill him!

71
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:46,800
The third soul skill, teleportation.

72
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:03,350
Stop it. You're stepping out of line.

73
00:06:07,710 --> 00:06:08,800
Wu.

74
00:06:09,150 --> 00:06:09,760
I'm sorry.

75
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,080
I didn't mean to.

76
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,350
It's alright. Again.

77
00:06:16,470 --> 00:06:18,880
No, you almost got hurt.

78
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:21,370
I feel like I'm about to break through
the level 50 bottleneck.

79
00:06:21,390 --> 00:06:23,680
The normal training is no longer
of much use to me.

80
00:06:24,070 --> 00:06:25,200
Thank goodness for Erming.

81
00:06:25,210 --> 00:06:27,150
He used his gravity control field
to pressure me.

82
00:06:27,170 --> 00:06:28,940
That helped me
to concentrate my soul power.

83
00:06:28,950 --> 00:06:31,120
It's the push I need
to finally reach level 50.

84
00:06:31,470 --> 00:06:32,120
But...

85
00:06:36,270 --> 00:06:37,200
San.

86
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:54,950
San.

87
00:06:56,030 --> 00:06:57,950
(I don't know what you've been through,)

88
00:06:58,710 --> 00:07:00,390
(nor what I could do for you.)

89
00:07:01,590 --> 00:07:03,640
But whenever I was powerless,

90
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,640
I would think of a children's song

91
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:07,350
my mother used to sing

92
00:07:07,710 --> 00:07:09,120
for me in the past.

93
